metadata.name: meanwhile the world went on
metadata.description:
Meanwhile the world went on: the dream state personified.  

From a series of works comprising Meta.morphosis, an infrared medium format photographic essay. 

Meta.morpohsis evokes a suspended state and the delicate transitions we make between worlds, real and imagined. Between lives lived digitally and our lived experience of the natural world. Between lucid thought and insanity.
